gs:LocationThe brick home of [[Rose & Thorn]] near the [[Gates of Barovia]]."},{"title":"Ireena Kolyana","slug":"__NPCs__Greater++++Barovia__Ireena++++Kolyana","shortSummary":"tags:NPCAdopted daughter of [[Kolyan Indirovich]], bitten by a vampyr."},{"title":"Kolyan Indirovich","slug":"__NPCs__Greater++++Barovia__Kolyan++++Indirovich","shortSummary":"tags:NPCOnce Burgomaster of [[Barovia]]. Seems to have prompted [[Barovia]]'s sealing after his adopted daughter, [[Ireena Kolyana]], was bitten by a vampyr."},{"title":"Strahd von Zarovich","slug":"__NPCs__Greater++++Barovia__Strahd++++von++++Zarovich","shortSummary":"aliases:Strahd\ntags:NPCDread Lord and Master of [[Barovia]], a vampyr, likely trapped there after [[Kolyan Indirovich]] called for [[Barovia]] to be sealed away following [[Strahd von Zarovich|Strahd]]'s attack on his adopted daughter [[Ireena Kolyana]]. At least one man believed him summonable through"},{"title":"Arrigal","slug":"__NPCs__Starting++++Caravan__Arrigal","shortSummary":"tags:NPCLeader of the starting caravan. Recruited many of the party to join."},{"title":"Elisabeth Durst","slug":"__NPCs__The++++Death++++House__Elisabeth++++Durst","shortSummary":"tags:NPC\nLocation: \"[[The Death House]]\"Mother to [[Rose & Thorn]]."},{"title":"Gustav Durst","slug":"__NPCs__The++++Death++++House__Gustav++++Durst","shortSummary":"tags:NPC\nLocation: \"[[The Death House]]\"Father with [[Elisabeth Durst]] to [[Rose & Thorn]]. Father with [[Margaret]] to a [[Walter Durst|stillborn son]]."},{"title":"Margaret","slug":"__NPCs__The++++Death++++House__Margaret","shortSummary":"tags:NPC\nLocation: \"[[The Death House]]\"Nursemaid to [[Durst Family]], mother of an illegitimate [[Walter Durst|stillborn son]] sired by [[Gustav Durst]]. Found as a spirit in the nursery of [[The Death House]]. Told the party not to touch the body of her child"},{"title":"Rose & Thorn","slug":"__NPCs__The++++Death++++House__Rose++++ambersand++++Thorn","shortSummary":"tags:NPC\nLocation: \"[[The Death House]]\"Full names Rosavelda Durst and Thornboldte Durst, children living in [[The Death House]]. Thorn clutches a doll and weeps ceaslessly, seems to be about 7 year old. Rose, 10, is more put together."},{"title":"Walter Durst","slug":"__NPCs__The++++Death++++House__Walter++++Durst","shortSummary":"tags:NPC\nLocation: \"[[The Death House]]\"\naliases:Stillborn babyStillborn sonStillborn son of [[Gustav Durst]] and the [[Margaret]]."},{"title":"Arden","slug":"__PCs__Arden","shortSummary":"aliases:\nPlayer: Zach\nClass: Paladin\nSubclass: Oath of Redemption\nSpecies: Half-Elf\ntags:PCHalf-Elf follower of [[Ilmater]]."},{"title":"Ellory Vellum","slug":"__PCs__Ellory++++Vellum","shortSummary":"aliases:Ellory\nPlayer: Tommy\nClass: Sorcerer\nSubclass: Divine Soul\nSpecies: Human\ntags:PCLeatherworker's apprentice."},{"title":"H of H","slug":"__PCs__H++++of++++H","shortSummary":"Player: Freddy\nClass: Cleric\nSubclass: Knowledge Domain\nSpecies: Human\ntags:PCFollower of [[Ilmater]]."},{"title":"Mercurie Slypher","slug":"__PCs__Mercurie++++Slypher","shortSummary":"aliases:Mercurie\nPlayer: Colin\nClass: Warlock\nSubclass: Pact of the Fiend\nSpecies: Tiefling\ntags:PCTiefling that once served in the armies of the nine hells."},{"title":"Viscero","slug":"__PCs__Viscero","shortSummary":"aliases:Viscero\nPlayer: Joey\nClass: Wizard\nSubclass: School of Illusion\nSpecies: Human\ntags:PCHas numerous scars around his mouth and his lips don't move when he speaks. Quite proficient with illusion magic."},{"title":"Session 1 - Death House Disco","slug":"__Session++++Notes__Session++++1++++-++++Death++++House++++Disco","shortSummary":"Session Date: 12/22/2024\ntags:SummaryCampaign starts with a group of travelers headed through some foggy woods as part of a caravan led by [[Arrigal]]at night [[Mercurie Slypher]], [[Arden]], [[H of H]], [[Viscero]], and [[Ellory Vellum]] huddle around a campfire. [[Arrigal]] checks up"},{"title":"Session 2 - Waltuh","slug":"__Session++